tasks.description:
Create infra/mysql/init/01_init.sql. This script runs automatically on first container startup via docker-entrypoint-initdb.d. It should:

- Create each service database if it does not exist, e.g.:
  CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS loanflow_loan_db CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;

- Grant the application user full privileges on each service database:
  GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON loanflow_loan_db.* TO '${DATABASE_USER}'@'%';
  FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

As additional services requiring MySQL are added, their databases are appended to this script.
